items.title: Muhurat Trading 2024 Live | Sensex, Nifty set to start special trading session for Samvat 2081
items.description: Stock Market LIVE Updates |  All three U.S. stock indexes closed lower on Thursday after Microsoft and Meta Platforms highlighted growing artificial intelligence costs that could hit their earnings, curbing enthusiasm for megacaps that have fueled the market rally this year. The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell 378.08 points, or 0.90%, to 41,763.46. The S&P 500 lost 108.22 points, or 1.86%, at 5,705.45 and the Nasdaq Composite dropped 512.78 points, or 2.76%, to 18,095.15.
